Functional:
----------

1) FUnction componet are made up of simmple function
2) You should use function component as much as possible.
3) In function there is absence of this keyword which is major differncetiator.
4) function component are without complicate logic and responsible for UI.
5) FUNCTIONAL COMPONET are also called as stateless/dump/presentational componet.


Class Component:
---------------
1) It has more features.
2) They can maintain there own privavte data called as state.
3) complex UI Logic 
4) provide lifecycle hooks.
5) CLASS COMPONET are also called as stateful/smart/container component.